ArcPlayer.description: An arc of Lightning stretches from the caster to a targeted enemy and Chains on to other nearby enemies. Shocked enemies Hit release damaging pulses.
ArcPlayer.name: Arc

ArchmagePlayer.description: While active, causes your Non-Channelling Spells to cost additional mana and deal extra Lightning damage, both based on your maximum Mana.
ArchmagePlayer.name: Archmage

ArcticArmourPlayer.description: While active, conjures an icy barrier that gains stages over time. While the barrier has stages, Melee Attacks that hit you will remove a stage to cause a burst of ice that deals Cold Spell damage to the attacker.
ArcticArmourPlayer.name: Arctic Armour

BallLightningPlayer.description: Fire a slow-moving orb Projectile that moves through enemies. The orb itself does not Hit enemies, but repeatedly shoots bolts of Lightning at nearby targets.
BallLightningPlayer.name: Ball Lightning

BlasphemyPlayer.description: Turn socketed Curse skills into vile Auras, applying their effects to all nearby enemies.
BlasphemyPlayer.name: Blasphemy

BlazingClusterPlayer.description: Conjure a blazing Ember that hovers above you. After a short duration, the Ember launches at an enemy, dealing Fire damage in an area on impact and prioritising the last enemy targeted. Recasting this spell resets the duration for all active Embers. Multiple Embers fired in the same Fusillade will attempt to target different enemies.
BlazingClusterPlayer.name: Ember Fusillade

BlinkPlayer.description: While active, replaces your dodge roll with a short-cooldown Spell that allows you to tunnel through space, instantly reappearing a medium distance away.
BlinkPlayer.name: Blink

BlinkReservationPlayer.description: While active, replaces your dodge roll with a short-cooldown Spell that allows you to tunnel through space, instantly reappearing a medium distance away.
BlinkReservationPlayer.name: Blink

BoneBlastPlayer.description: Conjure a circle of ritual inscriptions that last for a short duration. When the duration ends, spikes of bone erupt from enemies in the area, damaging them and potentially causing Bleeding.
BoneBlastPlayer.name: Bone Blast

BoneCagePlayer.description: Raise a ring of bone spikes around you. The spikes are destroyed when enemies touch them, damaging and Pinning those enemies.
BoneCagePlayer.name: Bone Cage

BoneOfferingPlayer.description:
Impale a Skeleton on a bone spike to shield your Minions while the spike remains. The shield absorbs all damage from the next Hit each Minion takes, then explodes.

The bone spike is itself a Minion, and shields itself. If it dies, shields on your other Minions disappear.
BoneOfferingPlayer.name: Bone Offering

BonestormPlayer.description: Channel to conjure a swarm of bone spikes in the air, then release to fire them at enemies and explode. Shrapnel Impales Enemies Hit, causing subsequent Attack Hits against those targets to deal extra Damage. Consumes your Power Charges to cause much larger explosions.
BonestormPlayer.name: Bonestorm

ChargeInfusionPlayer.description: While active, you gain powerful Buffs based on your active Charges. However, maintaining the Buff Consumes Charges every few seconds.
ChargeInfusionPlayer.name: Charge Infusion

ChargedStaffPlayer.description: Consume all Power Charges to infuse your Quarterstaff with electricity, adding Lightning damage and a Lightning shockwave to your Quarterstaff Attacks. Reusing this skill while the Buff is active adds to the Buff's duration and damage.
ChargedStaffPlayer.name: Charged Staff

ColdSnapPlayer.description: Shatter the frost on a Frozen enemy, Consuming the Freeze to deal a large amount of Cold Damage to enemies caught in the blast. Can also be cast on a Frostbolt to cause it to explode immediately. Any Frozen enemies hit by the Frostbolt's explosion will be dealt Cold Snap's damage and have their Freeze Consumed.
ColdSnapPlayer.name: Cold Snap

CometPlayer.description: Call down a mass of ice from the sky, dealing high damage at the targeted location. Targeting close to you will cause you to jump back as you cast.
CometPlayer.name: Comet

ConductivityPlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, lowering their Lightning Resistance.
ConductivityPlayer.name: Conductivity

ContagionPlayer.description:
Afflict a single enemy with a Debuff that deals Chaos damage over time. If the enemy dies while affected by Contagion, it and all other Chaos damage over time Debuffs spread to nearby enemies and refresh their durations. Reanimating or detonating a corpse affected by Contagion will cause the Minion or explosion to
spread Contagion on hit.
ContagionPlayer.name: Contagion

ConvalescencePlayer.description: While active, grants a skill that you can use to instantly begin Recharging Energy Shield and gain a Buff for a duration that prevents that Recharge being interrupted. The Buff is removed at maximum Energy Shield and the skill cannot be used while Energy Shield is full.
ConvalescencePlayer.name: Convalescence

CorpseCloudPlayer.description: Consume a Corpse to create a cloud of flammable Poisonous gas. Any Burning effects or Detonator skills will explode the gas cloud, creating a fiery explosion.
CorpseCloudPlayer.name: Decompose

DarkEffigyPlayer.description: Raise a Totem that bombards enemies afflicted by Chaos damage over time Debuffs.
DarkEffigyPlayer.name: Dark Effigy

DarkEffigyProjectilePlayer.description: Fire a Projectile at every nearby enemy that is afflicted by a Chaos damage over time Debuff. Fires multiple Projectiles at enemies afflicted by multiple Debuffs, but Projectile count cannot be otherwise modified.
DarkEffigyProjectilePlayer.name: Vile Effusion

DespairPlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, lowering their Chaos Resistance.
DespairPlayer.name: Despair

DetonateDeadPlayer.description: Cause a Corpse to violently explode, damaging surrounding enemies.
DetonateDeadPlayer.name: Detonate Dead

DisciplinePlayer.description: Emit an Aura that grants you and Allies in your Presence additional Total Energy Shield.
DisciplinePlayer.name: Discipline

ElementalConfluxPlayer.description: Tap into a current of raw and unpredictable Elemental power, causing you to deal greatly more damage of a randomly chosen Element. The Element affected changes frequently, though the same Element can be affected multiple times in succession.
ElementalConfluxPlayer.name: Elemental Conflux

EnfeeblePlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, making them deal less damage.
EnfeeblePlayer.name: Enfeeble

EssenceDrainPlayer.description: Fire a Projectile that applies a powerful Chaos damage over time debuff to enemies it hits.
EssenceDrainPlayer.name: Essence Drain

EyeOfWinterPlayer.description: Fire a single Eye Projectile which does not Hit enemies. The Eye constantly releases damaging shard Projectiles in a spiral as it flies, plus an extra burst of shards at the end of its flight. If the Eye passes over an Elemental ground surface or Orb, it will take on that surface's effect causing shards to deal more damage of the corresponding Type.
EyeOfWinterPlayer.name: Eye of Winter

FallingThunderPlayer.description: Infuse your Quarterstaff with electrical energy, then Slam the ground to deal damage in a large cone in front of you. Consumes your Power Charges to fire Lightning Projectiles forwards from the impact.
FallingThunderPlayer.name: Falling Thunder

FireballPlayer.description: Launch a large ball of Fire which explodes on impact, creating a nova of smaller firebolts.
FireballPlayer.name: Fireball

FireboltPlayer.description: Launch a fiery Projectile towards a target. The Projectile explodes on impact, damaging foes in a small area.
FireboltPlayer.name: Firebolt

FirestormPlayer.description: Rain flaming bolts over the targeted area. Ignites on enemies in front of you are Consumed to fuel the Firestorm by creating improved bolts.
FirestormPlayer.name: Firestorm

FlameWallPlayer.description: Create a wall of Fire in front of the character, which Ignites everything within its area. Any Projectiles fired through the wall by you and Allies deal added Fire damage and inflict the Ignite on hit.
FlameWallPlayer.name: Flame Wall

FlameblastPlayer.description: Channel to build destructive energy around you or a targeted Solar Orb. Releasing the energy causes a devastating explosion that is larger and more intense the longer you Channelled for.
FlameblastPlayer.name: Flameblast

FlammabilityPlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, lowering their Fire Resistance.
FlammabilityPlayer.name: Flammability

FlickerStrikePlayer.description: Teleport to a enemy and Strike them. Consumes Power Charges to perform additional teleporting Strikes on nearby enemies.
FlickerStrikePlayer.name: Flicker Strike

FreezingMarkPlayer.description: Mark a target, making them more susceptible to being Frozen. When the Marked target dies, a Cold nova erupts from their corpse. This nova does not use your Weapon Damage, and instead uses its own base Attack Damage.
FreezingMarkPlayer.name: Freezing Mark

FreezingShardsPlayer.description: Launch icy Projectiles in a sweeping arc. Multiple Projectiles can hit the same enemy.
FreezingShardsPlayer.name: Freezing Shards

FrostBombPlayer.description: Create a pulsing Orb of frost. Each pulse inflicts Cold Exposure on nearby enemies. When the Orb's duration ends, it explodes, dealing Cold damage to surrounding enemies.
FrostBombPlayer.name: Frost Bomb

FrostWallPlayer.description: Create a wall of Ice Crystals which holds back enemies. The Crystals explode if sufficiently damaged, or if pushed hard enough, damaging nearby enemies.
FrostWallPlayer.name: Frost Wall

FrostboltPlayer.description: Fire a slow-moving Piercing Projectile that leaves a wake of Chilled Ground, deals Cold damage and explodes on colliding with terrain.
FrostboltPlayer.name: Frostbolt

FrozenLocusPlayer.description: Leap backward and crack the ground with your staff to call forth an Ice Crystal, which creates Chilled Ground around it and can be damaged by you and enemies. If the Crystal is destroyed it causes an icy explosion that deals Attack damage but does not use your weapon's damage. This skill can be used while using other skills.
FrozenLocusPlayer.name: Frozen Locus

GaleStrikePlayer.description: Batter enemies at range by generating a gust of wind as you swing. Enemies will be Knocked Back based on how close they are to you.
GaleStrikePlayer.name: Wind Blast

GalvanicFieldPlayer.description: Gain a Buff that boosts your Shock chance. Shocking an enemy consumes the Buff to attach an Orb of electricity to that enemy. The Orb fires bolts of electricity at nearby enemies until it expires.
GalvanicFieldPlayer.name: Galvanic Field

GatheringStormPlayer.description: Flip backward and Channel to charge your Quarterstaff with Lightning. Releasing dashes towards the target location, damaging enemies along the way. Releasing with perfect timing performs a Lightning-infused dash that releases shockwaves from enemies you dash through and leaves a trail of Shocked Ground in your wake. This skill cannot be Ancestrally Boosted.
GatheringStormPlayer.name: Gathering Storm

GhostDancePlayer.description: While active, causes you to periodically gain Ghost Shrouds. If you are Hit while you have a Ghost Shroud, it is immediately consumed to recover Energy Shield based on your Evasion.
GhostDancePlayer.name: Ghost Dance

GlacialCascadePlayer.description: Sweep your Quarterstaff upwards, releasing an icy fissure which deals damage in a series of bursts culminating in a large spike. Frozen enemies hit by the final spike are dealt heavy damage but the Freeze is Consumed. Ice Crystals hit by the final spike explode.
GlacialCascadePlayer.name: Glacial Cascade

GrimFeastPlayer.description: This skill is currently disabled. We will rework and reenable it soon!
GrimFeastPlayer.name: Grim Feast

HandOfChayulaPlayer.description: Dash to an enemy and Strike them with an unarmed Attack, applying socketed Curses and triggering socketed Marks with reduced effect. This skill always Strikes with your bare fist, even if you have a Quarterstaff equipped.
HandOfChayulaPlayer.name: Hand of Chayula

HeraldOfIcePlayer.description: While active, Shattering an enemy with a non-Herald Attack Hit will cause an icy explosion that deals Attack damage to surrounding enemies.
HeraldOfIcePlayer.name: Herald of Ice

HexblastPlayer.description: Detonate a Curse on every enemy in an area, causing explosions of Chaos damage but removing the Curse. Can only detonate Curses for which at least half of the duration has expired.
HexblastPlayer.name: Hexblast

HypothermiaPlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, lowering their Cold Resistance.
HypothermiaPlayer.name: Hypothermia

IceNovaPlayer.description: Conjure a wave of ice in all directions, Knocking Back enemies based on how close they are to you. Casting Ice Nova targeting near a Frostbolt Projectile will cause it to originate from the Frostbolt instead of you.
IceNovaPlayer.name: Ice Nova

IceStrikePlayer.description: Perform a fast icy Strike. Using this Attack three times in quick succession causes a final strike that is slower and more powerful.
IceStrikePlayer.name: Ice Strike

IncineratePlayer.description: Conjure a torrent of Fire from your hand, Igniting enemies in front of you. The flames grow stronger the longer you Channel for, and at maximum strength also apply stacking Fire Exposure and creating Ignited Ground.
IncineratePlayer.name: Incinerate

KillingPalmPlayer.description: Dash to an enemy and Strike them with an unarmed Attack, Culling enemies if their life is low enough. Each enemy killed by this strike grants a Power Charge. Enemies around you that can be Culled will be highlighted. This skill always Strikes with your bare fist, even if you have a Quarterstaff equipped.
KillingPalmPlayer.name: Killing Palm

LightningBoltPlayer.description: Call down a Shocking bolt of Lightning to strike enemies in a small area.
LightningBoltPlayer.name: Lightning Bolt

LightningConduitPlayer.description: Call down lightning to hit all enemies in a cone in front of you. Deals significantly more damage to Shocked enemies but Consumes Shock from them after damaging them. If a Shock is Consumed, additional lightning bolts are distributed among the targets hit. Targeting close to you will cause you to jump back as you cast.
LightningConduitPlayer.name: Lightning Conduit

LightningWarpPlayer.description: Teleport inside the target's body, causing it to violently explode. Highlights enemies that can be Culled, and can only be used on these enemies or Ball Lightning Projectiles. The target is destroyed, and the explosion deals Lightning Damage to surrounding enemies. If targeting an enemy the explosion also creates Shocked Ground.
LightningWarpPlayer.name: Lightning Warp

LingeringIllusionPlayer.description: While active, creates a short-lived illusory copy of yourself whenever you dodge roll. The copy can be damaged by enemies, and copies that are destroyed by an enemy will grant you a Power Charge.
LingeringIllusionPlayer.name: Lingering Illusion

LivingBombPlayer.description: Plant a seed of Fire inside an enemy, which grows over a duration. When the duration expires, the seed explodes, damaging the enemy and all other enemies nearby.
LivingBombPlayer.name: Living Bomb

MalicePlayer.description: While active, emits an Aura that continuously inflicts Critical Weakness on enemies in your Presence.
MalicePlayer.name: Malice

ManaDrainPlayer.description: Siphon power from an enemy, briefly Hindering them and Leeching Mana.
ManaDrainPlayer.name: Mana Drain

ManaRemnantsPlayer.description: Conjure surging arcane energy to restore your Mana. While active, enemies you kill affected by Elemental Ailments have a chance to spawn a Mana Remnant, and Critically Hitting a target with Elemental Ailments spawns a Mana Remnant every few seconds. Picking up a Mana Remnant grants you Mana which can Overflow maximum Mana.
ManaRemnantsPlayer.name: Mana Remnants

ManaTempestPlayer.description: Create a storm of arcane energies that Empowers your Mana-costing Spells while you remain inside it. Maintaining the storm constantly drains your Mana, and each Spell you cast causes it to drain faster. The storm will dissipate when you exit it or run out of Mana.
ManaTempestPlayer.name: Mana Tempest

MantraOfDestructionPlayer.description:
Build Combo by successfully Striking Enemies with other skills. After reaching maximum Combo, use this skill to Empower your next Quarterstaff Attack, causing it to deal additional Chaos damage. Each kill with the Empowered Attack grants
Purple Flames of Chayula for a duration.
MantraOfDestructionPlayer.name: Mantra of Destruction

MetaBarrierInvocationPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when your Energy Shield is damaged by Enemy Hits. Using the Invocation once sufficient Energy is gathered will consume the Energy to trigger socketed Spells, and can trigger them multiple times if it has enough Energy.
MetaBarrierInvocationPlayer.name: Barrier Invocation

MetaCastOnCritPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Critically Hit enemies and triggers socketed Spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnCritPlayer.name: Cast on Critical

MetaCastOnDodgePlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you dodge roll and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnDodgePlayer.name: Cast on Dodge

MetaCastOnFreezePlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Freeze enemies and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnFreezePlayer.name: Cast on Freeze

MetaCastOnIgnitePlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Ignite enemies and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnIgnitePlayer.name: Cast on Ignite

MetaCastOnMinionDeathPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when one of your Persistent Minions is Killed, and triggers socketed Spells upon reaching maximum Energy. Very underlevelled Minions will incur an Energy generation penalty. Cannot socket Spells which create Minions.
MetaCastOnMinionDeathPlayer.name: Cast on Minion Death

MetaCastOnShockPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Shock enemies and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnShockPlayer.name: Cast on Shock

MetaElementalInvocationPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Freeze, Shock or Ignite an enemy. Using the Invocation once sufficient Energy is gathered will consume the Energy to trigger socketed Spells, and can trigger them multiple times if it has enough Energy.
MetaElementalInvocationPlayer.name: Elemental Invocation

MetaReapersInvocationPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you kill an enemy with a Melee Attack. Using the Invocation once sufficient Energy is gathered will consume the Energy to trigger socketed Spells, and can trigger them multiple times if it has enough Energy.
MetaReapersInvocationPlayer.name: Reaper's Invocation

OrbOfStormsPlayer.description: Create an Orb of electricity that fires Chaining Lightning bolts at nearby enemies.
OrbOfStormsPlayer.name: Orb of Storms

PainOfferingPlayer.description:
Skewer a Skeleton on a bone spike to send nearby Minions into a frenzy as long as the spike remains, making their skills faster and harder hitting.

The bone spike is itself a Minion. If it dies, the effect ends immediately.
PainOfferingPlayer.name: Pain Offering

PowerSiphonPlayer.description: Attempt to rip the lifeforce from an enemy. Enemies within Culling range will be highlighted and instantly killed on Hit, granting a Power Charge. Can only target Enemies in Culling range.
PowerSiphonPlayer.name: Power Siphon

ProfaneRitualPlayer.description: Mark a Corpse with a profane rune, dealing Chaos damage over time to nearby enemies. When the ritual is complete the Corpse is consumed and you gain a Power Charge.
ProfaneRitualPlayer.name: Profane Ritual

PurityOfFirePlayer.description: Emit an Aura that boosts the Fire Resistance of you and Allies in your Presence.
PurityOfFirePlayer.name: Purity of Fire

PurityOfIcePlayer.description: Emit an Aura that boosts the Cold Resistance of you and Allies in your Presence.
PurityOfIcePlayer.name: Purity of Ice

PurityOfLightningPlayer.description: Emit an Aura that boosts the Lightning Resistance of you and Allies in your Presence.
PurityOfLightningPlayer.name: Purity of Lightning

RagingSpiritsPlayer.description: While active, Fire Spells you use yourself will also summon Raging Spirits, which are short-lived flaming skulls that rush at nearby enemies and rapidly Attack them. Enemies will not directly engage these Minions, and can pass through them.
RagingSpiritsPlayer.name: Raging Spirits

RaiseZombiePlayer.description: Consume a Corpse or Power Charge to create a short-lived Zombie. Zombies created from Power Charges are Empowered.
RaiseZombiePlayer.name: Raise Zombie

SacrificePlayer.description: While active, your undead Reviving Minions can be used in place of Corpses by your skills, but your Minions Revive more slowly.
SacrificePlayer.name: Sacrifice

ShatteringPalmPlayer.description: Dash to an enemy and Strike them with an Unarmed Attack that manifests a wave of cold, coating nearby enemies in shards of ice. Dealing enough damage to these enemies will shatter the shards, causing an icy explosion that deals Attack damage. This skill always Strikes with your bare fist, even if you have a Quarterstaff equipped.
ShatteringPalmPlayer.name: Shattering Palm

ShockNovaPlayer.description: Unleash a Nova of Lightning damage to Electrocute enemies.
ShockNovaPlayer.name: Shock Nova

SigilOfPowerPlayer.description: Place a Sigil on the ground, providing a powerful Spell Damage Buff to you and Allies while standing in it. The Buff becomes more powerful the more mana you spend while standing in the Sigil.
SigilOfPowerPlayer.name: Sigil of Power

SiphoningStrikePlayer.description: Dash to a target and Strike them with your Quarterstaff. If the target is Shocked, consumes their Shock to release a Lightning shockwave around the target and grant you a Power Charge. This skill cannot be Ancestrally Boosted.
SiphoningStrikePlayer.name: Siphoning Strike

SolarOrbPlayer.description: Create a fiery Orb that periodically releases fiery pulses. Enemies that are very close to the Orb are Ignited.
SolarOrbPlayer.name: Solar Orb

SoulOfferingPlayer.description:
Skewer a Skeleton on a bone spike, granting you a powerful Spell damage Buff as long as the spike remains. Does not affect your Minions.

The bone spike is itself a Minion. If it dies, the effect ends immediately.
SoulOfferingPlayer.name: Soul Offering

SparkPlayer.description: Launch a spray of sparking Projectiles that travel erratically along the ground until they hit an enemy or expire.
SparkPlayer.name: Spark

StaggeringPalmPlayer.description: Dash to an enemy and Strike them with an Unarmed Attack. Heavy Stunning an enemy with this Skill grants you a Buff that causes your Quarterstaff and Unarmed Attacks to also fire Projectiles for a short duration. Enemies which are Primed for Stun will instantly be Heavily Stunned. This skill always Strikes with your bare fist, even if you have a Quarterstaff equipped.
StaggeringPalmPlayer.name: Staggering Palm

StormWavePlayer.description: Sweep your Quarterstaff, projecting a bolt of Lightning through the ground in a long fissure ahead of you.
StormWavePlayer.name: Storm Wave

SummonSkeletalArsonistsPlayer.description: Activate to summon bomb-throwing, Reviving Skeletal Arsonists that can detonate other Minions on Command.
SummonSkeletalArsonistsPlayer.name: Skeletal Arsonist Minion

SummonSkeletalBrutesPlayer.description: Activate to summons hard-hitting, Reviving Skeletal Brutes that can Stun Primed enemies.
SummonSkeletalBrutesPlayer.name: Skeletal Brute Minion

SummonSkeletalClericsPlayer.description: Activate to summon Reviving Skeletal Clerics that heal other minions and revive fallen Skeletons.
SummonSkeletalClericsPlayer.name: Skeletal Cleric Minion

SummonSkeletalFrostMagesPlayer.description: Activate to summon Reviving Skeletal Frost Mages that can be Commanded to cast icy explosions.
SummonSkeletalFrostMagesPlayer.name: Skeletal Frost Mage Minion

SummonSkeletalReaversPlayer.description: Activate to summon aggressive, Reviving Skeletal Reavers that can enrage on Command.
SummonSkeletalReaversPlayer.name: Skeletal Reaver Minion

SummonSkeletalSnipersPlayer.description: Activate to summon long-ranged, Reviving Skeletal Snipers that can fire a gas arrow on Command.
SummonSkeletalSnipersPlayer.name: Skeletal Sniper Minion

SummonSkeletalStormMagesPlayer.description: Activate to summon Reviving Skeletal Storm Mages that can call down a lightning storm on dead Skeletons on Command.
SummonSkeletalStormMagesPlayer.name: Skeletal Storm Mage Minion

SummonSkeletalWarriorsPlayer.description: Activate to summon Reviving Skeletal Warriors.
SummonSkeletalWarriorsPlayer.name: Skeletal Warrior Minion

SummonSpectrePlayer.description: Summon the spirit of the bound monster as a Reviving Minion.
SummonSpectrePlayer.name: Spectre: {0}

TempestBellPlayer.description: Build Combo by successfully Striking Enemies with other skills. After reaching maximum Combo, use this skill to cause the Bell on your staff to grow to massive size as you drop it on the ground. The Bell damages enemies on impact and can be Hit by your skills, creating a damaging shockwave. Elemental Ailments applied to the Bell cause its shockwaves to deal extra damage of the corresponding type, and Hits which would have caused Knockback increase the area of effect of the shockwaves.
TempestBellPlayer.name: Tempest Bell

TempestFlurryPlayer.description: Perform a series of aggressive Strikes. When used in quick succession, the third use Strikes three times, and the fourth use performs a Final Strike that calls down a powerful Shocking bolt.
TempestFlurryPlayer.name: Tempest Flurry

TemporalChainsPlayer.description: Curse all enemies in an area, Slowing them and making other effects on them expire more slowly.
TemporalChainsPlayer.name: Temporal Chains

UnearthPlayer.description: Raise spikes of bone from the earth in front of you, damaging enemies. The bones of Corpses in the area are ripped out and reassembled into short-lived Bone Construct Minions that fight for you.
UnearthPlayer.name: Unearth

UnleashPlayer.description: Infuse yourself with temporal magic for a short duration, Empowering the next Spell you cast to repeat multiple times. Cannot Empower Channelling Skills or Skills with a Cooldown.
UnleashPlayer.name: Unleash

VaultingImpactPlayer.description: Leap forward and Slam the ground, sending out a Stunning shockwave that is especially potent against Dazed enemies.
VaultingImpactPlayer.name: Vaulting Impact

VolatileDeadPlayer.description: Consume a Corpse to create a fireball that seeks out enemies and explodes.
VolatileDeadPlayer.name: Volatile Dead

VulnerabilityPlayer.description: Curse all targets in an area after a short delay, making Hits against them ignore a portion of their Armour.
VulnerabilityPlayer.name: Vulnerability

WaveOfFrostPlayer.description: Flip backwards and send forth a Freezing wave in front of you.
WaveOfFrostPlayer.name: Wave of Frost

WeaponGrantedChaosboltPlayer.description: Fire a burst of Chaos energy at the target.
WeaponGrantedChaosboltPlayer.name: Chaos Bolt

WhirlingAssaultPlayer.description: Advance while hitting enemies around you with a series of spinning Strikes.
WhirlingAssaultPlayer.name: Whirling Assault

WitherPlayer.description: Channel a debilitating hex that Withers enemies in the area.
WitherPlayer.name: Wither

WitheringPresencePlayer.description: While active, emits an Aura that periodically Withers enemies in your Presence.
WitheringPresencePlayer.name: Withering Presence
